Simple really – to sharpen our focus on customers of Marmon Foodservice and The Marmon brands we support: What We Do At Marmon Link, we want to help operators make the absolute most out of the significant equipment investments they’ve made to service their In short, we connect purchase to From the very beginning of the equipment’s lifecycle through the end, Marmon Link will offer the single biggest selection of replacement parts, technical support and customer service to keep you up and And because we are part of Marmon, Marmon Link only offers genuine OEM This means that the parts critical to your equipment performance have gone through vigorous testing and quality assurance to ensure maximum uptime and Why Marmon Link? Quality and Innovation Marmon Foodservice and Beverage brands lead in equipment quality and innovation and are found in the nation s top restaurants and Marmon Link reflects those same characteristics in helping customers acquire and maintain their Replacement Parts We re your source for genuine Cornelius, Prince Castle, Silver King, Angelo Po, and Saber King replacement Because we re connected to these brands we offer the most comprehensive catalog of replacement parts with the best availability and pricing in the industry! Customer Care Our Customer Care team will continue to provide friendly and efficient service for ordering and other questions, and our website will offer the same great ordering experience you had on ! Technical Support We will continue to provide the industry s best technical support and warranty services for our Marmon Foodservice and Beverage Our network of Approved Service Agents allows us to dispatch warranty calls quickly, and our website has service manuals for your Marmon brand Marmon Link is a Responsible Business We take our responsibilities to the environment and the communities in which we operate very High standards of responsibility are, in our view, compatible with growth and business We put particular emphasis on ensuring that our management of social, environmental, and economic issues is aligned and integrated with the overall management of the business, and we call this “responsible ” As a Marmon Berkshire Hathaway company, Marmon Link maintains a firm commitment to ethical and legal business Marmon Link is dedicated to complying with all applicable laws and regulations and upholding a reputation for honesty and For more about Marmon, visit . Defective product injury claims typically fall into three categories of product liability: defects in manufacturing defective design or failure to provide adequate warnings or instructions concerning the proper use of the The plaintiff can generally sue for all financial losses caused by the defect, as well as any physical Any Party in the Product’s Chain of Distribution Could Be Liable for the The list of responsible parties may include: The product manufacturer, A manufacturer of component parts The wholesaler and The retail store that sold the product to the consumer If you Have been Injured by a Defective Product, Consult With an Experienced Personal Injury Lawyers at the Swigart Law Group have helped thousands of people in Please construct with us to find out how we can help Below is a form that you can fill out right now and have an attorney get back to you within business hours about your We will also discuss your case with you over the phone, and if you like, we can meet with you in person in our None of these options are exclusive – you can do as many or as few as you like, and we will charge you no attorneys’ fees or costs for that In short, we want it to be as easy as possible for you to evaluate whether or not you have a case, and if you do, take the best and most appropriate steps for you to How can we help you? About Us The National Institute for Undersea Vehicle Technologies (NIUVT) is a partnership between the University of Connecticut (UConn), University of Rhode Island (URI) and General Dynamics Electric Boat (EB) to enhance performance and reduce costs of the shipbuilding process while insuring that advanced technologies are implemented into the next generation and next platform of undersea NIUVT builds upon the experience and expertise of EB, UConn and URI to engage in research, technology transition, and workforce Through these activities, NIUVT will develop the personnel and knowledge needed to accelerate critical research and enhance superiority in submarine and other undersea vehicle Our Mission NIUVT is focused on institutionalizing the numerous research, technology transfer and workforce development activities in undersea vehicle technology that UConn, URI and EB have been pursuing for years, by: Conducting basic and applied RESEARCH on undersea vehicle technologies of strategic importance to the Navy through collaborative partnerships between the universities and industry Accelerating and facilitating TECHNOLOGY TRANSITION by ensuring relevant research can be more easily pulled into the shipbuilding industries and Supporting the WORKFORCE DEVELOPMENT of a technically competent and innovative next generation workforce through undergraduate STEM education and opportunities for engineers to obtain advanced degrees related to their Our Region The NIUVT is located at the UConn Avery Point campus, in close proximity to the naval submarine base in Groton, Connecticut, as well as to Electric Boat’s facilities in Connecticut and Rhode Island, UConn and URI main campuses, the Naval Undersea Warfare Center, the Naval War College, and approximately naval supply chain The NIUVT will leverage these major naval resources to enhance performance, introduce new technologies, and reduce costs associated with the design and construction of the next generation and next platform of undersea Contact Us Please contact the NIUVT , Professors Richard Christenson (UConn) and Arun Shukla (URI) if you are interested in being involved in this exciting Accelerating technology transition to the Navy through applied research and workforce © National Institute for Undersea Vehicle Technology UConn Site Index URI Site Index Contact Us University of Connecticut Avery Point Campus Shennecossett Road Groton, Connecticut URI Phone: UConn Phone:   Technology Transition | National Institute for Undersea Vehicle Technology (NIUVT) UCONN | University of Connecticut Menu Home About Workforce Development Research Capabilities Technology Transition News Contact Technology Transition The transfer of advanced technologies to the next vehicle or the next platform will be achieved by fostering an environment where basic and applied research is being pulled into the design and manufacturing process by EB and the companies in the supply chain as well as Navy labs NUWC and the Undersea Warfighting Development Center . While research is the core activity of the Institute, the most highly leveraged activity is the transition of technology advancements into major DoD acquisition Effectively transitioning research results is critical to provide a significant and positive impact on naval Members of the NIUVT are conducting basic and applied research hand in hand with industry partners to ensure that a path to transition The NIUVT is seeking to develop a framework to assist small businesses in the undersea technology area with: identifying and or further developing new technology team building and proposal preparation facilities to conduct SBIR or STTR research and transition of technologies and products to manufacturers and More details will be posted here as opportunities become Closely coupled to Workforce Development efforts, the technical training of students and knowledge gained in research in and projects by students who become employed in the undersea vehicle workforce serves as an effective means to transition technologies directly to the The Southern New England region is rich with industries supporting and providing undersea vehicles and technology to the Existing consortiums exist in the The NIUVT will work with Naval undersea consortiums to engage companies in the region in the activities and opportunities of the MURI: Tracking, Diagnosing, and Impeding Dielectric Breakdown in Polymers UConn was recently awarded a $7.5M MURI research grant from the Department of Defense Learn More Accelerating technology transition to the Navy through applied research and workforce © National Institute for Undersea Vehicle Technology UConn Site Index URI Site Index Contact Us University of Connecticut Avery Point Campus Shennecossett Road Groton, Connecticut URI Phon

Basic Coverages Normally Included Liability Liability coverage on your auto insurance is the most critical portion of your It is the coverage that pays out if you hurt someone in an accident, or if you cause any damage to property that doesn’t belong to When you consider the cost of medical bills, or the cost of cars on the road today, it’s no wonder why your liability insurance is the one portion of your auto insurance that you do not want to skimp Amazingly enough, your liability coverage is often times the cheapest part of your The cost to double, triple, or quadruple your auto liability coverage is For the same cost as a few Starbucks coffees for you and your friends, you could add ten times the amount of liability coverage to your When shopping for your auto insurance, be wary of any proposal or quote that offers the state minimum coverage for Tennessee minimum limits are 50K 15K What this means, is if you are involved in an accident that is your fault, and the other vehicle has three passengers who all have various levels of injuries, your auto insurance will only pay out $25,000 per person, as a maximum, however the policy will not pay any more than $50,000 for the entire The number in this liability limit represents the amount of coverage $15,000 for property damage that you are responsible for With the average cost of a new car above $36,000 , it’s is our professional recommendation to carry higher limits of property Any payout or settlement beyond those numbers will need to come from you These decisions are often made in a court setting when the other party has decided to sue With the high amount of fraud that takes place, it is a scary proposition to gamble with lower limits of Because of the low costs, and our belief that you deserve more, at The Client’s Insurance Agency, we will never offer an auto insurance proposal with inadequate, or state minimums for liability and property damage – Get a quote for better liability insurance here . whether efforts to attract customers will be paid САС will help you find out how effectively your marketing budget is Calculate how efficient a business САС helps to understand how productive a company Optimize marketing Expensive customers are a signal to review advertising expenses and reduce their How to calculate Customer acquisition cost To calculate the CAC using the following formula: САС = Sum of all expenses number of customers managed Technically, the formula is However, most marketers use the advanced formula to calculate CAC: To get the most accurate result, calculate CAC separately for each sale This makes it possible to understand which of the channels has the lowest CAC and where specifically it is worth increasing marketing investments: the more of the budget you allocate to the channels with a low cost of customer acquisition, the more users will be acquired without increasing the total Example of CAC calculation for Moving Company To see how the full formula works, we apply it on the example of a local Boston moving company We accept (30%) as a coefficient of a successful lead converting to a confirmed customer To begin, we write down all the initial Mental Health - Alter Health Group Home About Us Our Team Our Approach What We Treat Addiction Treatment Mental Health Treatment Insurance Verification Contact Us Careers Mental Health Treatment We’re dedicated to providing Californians with the resources they need to live their best, happiest One front of this effort is our dedication to providing mental health support, which is available at Alter Behavioral Health and BeWellLine . Alter is a premium mental health facility that serves adults on the autism spectrum as well as anxiety, depression, and various other On the other hand, BeWellLine is a telehealth company that’s now offering every Californian free counseling to help as the COVID crisis Behavioral health problems are far from rare, and the stress of recent years has caused them to grow even more Anxiety and stress disorders occur in over % of the population , and millions more suffer from other mental Alter Health Group has specialists suited to providing personalized care for all of the major behavioral health Mental Health Treatment Centers Alter Behavioral Heath Alter Behavioral Health is a primary care facility for neurodivergent people as well as those suffering from mental Alter’s major services include, but are not limited to: Adult autism care Attention Deficit Disorder Attention Deficit Hyperactive Disorder (ADD ADHD) treatment Bipolar Disorder treatment Anxiety treatment Depression treatment Obsessive Compulsive Disorder (OCD) treatment Schizophrenia Treatment Adult autism care Attention Deficit Disorder (ADD) treatment Attention Deficit Hyperactive Disorder (ADHD) treatment Bipolar Disorder treatment Anxiety treatment Depression treatment Obsessive Compulsive Disorder (OCD) treatment Schizophrenia Treatment Each of these conditions has its own nuances and challenges, and unique challenges for When it comes to autism, for instance, the emphasis lays on maximizing quality of life and identifying the support needs that will help the person succeed in their own When it comes to the mental illnesses that we treat, we offer a combination of therapy, education, and Cognitive behavioral therapy (CBT) is one of the cornerstones of the Alter approach to treating mental health CBT proven highly effective at treating depression, bipolar, and anxiety, but medication can sometimes improve the treatment On the other hand, many conditions such as schizophrenia only respond to specialty Nonetheless, Alter provides schizophrenia treatment with the latest antipsychotic drugs and robust education and While the latter two elements of the program won’t cure your disorder, they will help give you and your loved ones insight into this misunderstood, widely maligned Alter Behavioral Health works to provide Californians with the mental health care they need to manage any conditions they may have and live happy, fulfilling 4 Summit Irvine, CA Visit Website BeWellLine Heading to a clinic can be difficult for many people, from those who are particularly busy with work or child care or those who suffer from mobility Likewise, millions of Californians live in less densely populated towns and areas that lack access to mental health Worst of all, mental health care can often be too expensive for poorer Californians to BeWellLine is the answer to all of these problems, as it mobilizes experienced counselors, case managers, and local community members to provide phone and mental health As such, you can reach out for support and understanding from the comfort of your own In light of the stress of the COVID pandemic, we’ve also worked to make a baseline level of mental health services available to all BeWellLine is currently operating in a partnership with the state of California the FEMA Crisis Counselling Assistance and Training If you live in California, you’re already entitled to the benefits of this You can arrange to join six counseling sessions at no charge, which you’re free to arrange via webchat, telephone, or video While we normally arrange these sessions for groups, you can also arrange a session specifically for your own The ultimate goal of BeWellLine is to cut through the isolation that many of us are experiencing in The Best Image Search Tool - Where and Share Skip to content For Retailers Advertise with Us About Us Blog Where and Share For Retailers Advertise with Us About Us Blog by Trinity Wiles on June , A few weeks ago, at the MARS conference Amazon introduced their newest fashion search feature, StyleSnap allows users to upload an image and make a search from the mobile Amazon Amazon then uses deep learning to detect items within the image and finds the closest This feature isn’t new You may have seen or even used this feature before, just on a different I decided to review and compare the most popular in app image search features from (RewardStyle), Pinterest and Amazon . I uploaded the same image to every app to see which platform produced the most accurate The goal was to find dress in the image, using the search tool on each I started with an image I found on This was taken from the influencer and lifestyle bloggers’ page, . Brittany has followers on Instagram and ,916 followers on the After deciding on an image, I began to try each apps search Pinterest Amazon StyleSnap is the single largest influencer shopping channel and consumer media The app has millions of users and is a global place for discovering influencers and new The platform drives more than $1B in annual retail sales by uniting brands, influencers and To do a item image search, it is All you need to do is to have the app downloaded and set up on your The only issue for image searching is that the photo must be a “LIKEtoKNOW.it-enabled look”. This means that the native Instagram photo must have a link and “#liketkit” hashtag in the However, once the image is screenshotted is automatically matched to the Despite having limitations because of image qualifications, it is the most seamless search of all the However, the accuracy of the results surprised When I screenshotted the photo, these were the results that were matched from the The app failed to find the exact dress in the It came up with similar floral dresses but not the same This surprised me as selects their influencers and I assumed the results from the photo would be Pinterest The second image search I did was in Pinterest is a sharing platform for discovering anything from DIY projects, to education, to fashion and anything in To conduct an image search on Pinterest, you can simply do it by clicking the camera icon within the search From there, you can upload a screen shot from your camera Once I did that, here were my Pinterest, by far, had the most inaccurate results in comparison the searches on the other Amazon Lastly, I tried image searching on The amazon search had almost the same process as I clicked the camera in the search From there I went to “StyleSnap” and uploaded the I was extremely impressed with the Amazon found, what appears to be, the exact dress in the I was blown One other feature I liked about the Amazon search tool was that you could drag around the “box” to search different items within the For example, I could also scroll over the hat to find the complete Conclusion After trying out each image search, here is what I rank them on Amazon Pinterest Categories: Review Tags: No Tag Post navigation Previous post Our London NikeTown Flagship Review Post navigation Next post Weird Things Consumers Are Actually Paying For Comments are closed Search for: Mailchimp Signup Form Download Our Whitepaper on Safely Opening Fitting Rooms! What Types of Hemp Processing Can We Do? Before your harvest is ready for extraction, the hemp must be properly milled and Fortunately for our partner farmers who rely on us to handle their harvests, our advanced, combines take care of milling in the We only process milled material, so please visit our cultivation and harvesting page if you need harvesting As the other major step in hemp processing, drying is not where you want to cut When hemp is dried properly and quickly, the quality and size of your yield is On the other hand, you may experience spoilage, fungal mold, or bacterial contamination in hemp that is harvested too wet or dried too slowly and without proper In fact, the drying process is where our facilities truly With a capacity to dry up to ,000 wet pounds each hour, we are one of the few processors who can handle industrial Operating at this scale allows us to pass on big savings and critical efficiencies to our valued Biomass Processing Hemp biomass is plant matter that is left over once the hemp flower is removed, like stalks and Due to high levels of unmet demand for CBD and newer extraction technologies, what was once considered a “waste product” in conventional farming has now skyrocketed in See how our experts are helping partner farmers take advantage of their biomass to increase profits! Learn More How Does It Work? We can approach toll processing in several Typically, toll fees range from $0.75 to $2.50 a pound for drying and $25.00 to $35.00 a pound for This number will depend on the size and quality of your crop, your business goals, and external factors like market If you have already arranged a seller for your oil, then we return it to you as soon as payment is We also offer our toll split partners an option to divide the oil between both How we divvy it up will depend on the quality of your samples and the volume you need Experience The Arbor Vita8 Difference As the other major step in hemp processing, drying is not where you want to cut When hemp is dried properly and quickly, the quality and size of your yield is On the other hand, you may experience spoilage, fungal mold, or bacterial contamination in hemp that is harvested too wet or dried too slowly and without proper From seed to sale, we take pride in providing the most efficient and support for our partner farmers and In today’s booming (but underdeveloped) market, it is very difficult to find vendors who can even dry and process large quantities of hemp – let alone do it with dedication and Our focus is widening this bottleneck to make life easier for farmers and We want hemp farmers and manufacturers to be successful, not only because our success is intrinsically tied to yours, but also because we believe this crop is a valuable resource for Getting this resource from your farm and into the hands of those who need it doesn’t have to be a stressful, inefficient, or unprofitable We can say this confidently because we’ve put in the work, gone through the , and have the agricultural experience necessary to be To learn more about our partner farmer program, reach out Let’s get to work! When our faces are animated by our expressions, we develop forehead lines, brow furrows, crow’s feet, and bunny lines (the vertical lines across the bridge of the nose). To combat this, neuromodulators such as Botox and Dysport temporarily paralyze the corrugator, procerus, and orbicularis oculi muscles, all of which are responsible for horizontal surprise lines on the forehead, deep furrows—sometimes called “elevens”—between the brows, and crow’s Botox and Dysport block the nerve signals from the brain to these muscles, reducing activity and giving the skin the opportunity to Over time, wrinkles in the skin So if you’re concerned about fine lines and wrinkles around your eyes and forehead, but aren’t ready for a surgical treatment such as a facelift, either Botox or Dysport may be everything you Am I a Good Candidate? Most people concerned about forehead lines and wrinkles, brow furrows, or crow’s feet are good Those allergic to any ingredient in Botox or Dysport, have a skin infection in the treatment area, are pregnant or breastfeeding, or have a muscle or nerve condition may not be ideal patients for neuromodulator cosmetic How Long Do Botox or Dysport Injections Take? Botox and Dysport injections are one of the fastest treatments for forehead lines, brow furrows, and crow’s feet available Your session could be as quick as minutes, or, depending on the number of treatment areas, as long as How Quickly Will I See Results? The effects may extend beyond that for patients who’ve had repeated Botox or Dysport Is There Any Downtime?
